{"tid":2138243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙控稱留意中美潛在法規衝突　承認面對十分大挑戰","createTime":"2020-08-03T12:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T14:55:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4e83346e42fbd162e99f532fe62a491407c699a2","tid":2138243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541594-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541594-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0Oy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=32a7bf45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541594-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=29a3a51c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541594-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n滙控上半年股東應佔純利大跌近77%，繼續停派股息。香港區業務因為預期信貸損失及信貸減值急升，上半年稅前盈利按年倒退29%。<br />\n<br />\n面對集團捲入中美政治爭拗，管理層說，會尊重集團營運地點的法例法規，但承認銀行正面對十分大的挑戰，會留意中美之間潛在的法規衝突。"},{"pid":"051f0ee3604605c736ff0b342868e27f0512a6ef","tid":2138243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541610-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541610-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0Oy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=1a06ed85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541610-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8bf878f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541610-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n滙控財務總監邵偉信表示，集團預期全年<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">信貸損失準備或介乎80億至130億美元</span></span></strong>，連同疫情及地緣政治因素，或影響日後派息。<br />\n<br />\n他又估計，下半年淨利息收益率將會<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">進一步向下</span></span></strong>。"},{"pid":"d0aaae92b7870e80e3c736c0de7323f7010878ef","tid":2138243,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">滙控收市跌逾4%</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541560-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541560-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0Oy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=40e18613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541560-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d2964f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541560-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港股下跌，滙控上半年盈利表現差過市場預期，不利金融股同大市表現。恒生指數全日最多跌345點，收市跌137點，報24458點。主板成交1305億元。<br />\n<br />\n滙控一度跌穿33元「海嘯價」，低見32.95元，跌近6%，收市跌幅收窄至4.4%，報33.4元。恒生亦跌近3%收市。<br />\n<br />\n中電中期業績轉虧為盈，股價升近1%。"},{"pid":"ceca4394c5662afd9838c4ee4d4a393c1394e1b8","tid":2138243,"uid":29188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"仲想兩邊lam? 等睇兩邊得罪哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b3a513baa42fa7bce735be5deb0dbc2eaff9c0","tid":2138243,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceca4394c5662afd9838c4ee4d4a393c1394e1b8","tid":2138243,"uid":29188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"仲想兩邊lam? 等睇兩邊得罪哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"大是大非<br />\n<br />\n正義與邪惡<br />\n<br />\n真係無得企中間"},{"pid":"d2fdf15cc4b48e92dc59c0509dffc98befa2d87b","tid":2138243,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b3a513baa42fa7bce735be5deb0dbc2eaff9c0","tid":2138243,"uid